{"tid":2228600,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"正式收返毒撚係高質嘅言論","createTime":"2020-10-03T16:54:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-04T16:30:31.000Z","uid":200529,"like":15,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"af859808945440510c6be14625534612cb3c149c","tid":2228600,"uid":200529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T16:54:26.000Z","msg":"1. 識日文而有莫名嘅優越感 <br />\n識日文就以為自己天才 圍爐笑唔識日文嘅人 當你同佢地講英文又會集體笑你 如下圖<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YO7fVPe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYO7fVPe.png&h=bd0056d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pKLdHuf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpKLdHuf.png&h=6cb156b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 非常陰濕 喜歡集體欺凌恥笑<br />\n我就係好例子 明裏我差唔多每個po都會有人留垃圾留言攻擊我 對我嘅po評頭品足<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iVZh9as.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiVZh9as.png&h=62bd4b75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KaMDTB8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKaMDTB8.png&h=2b29ea09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n暗裏我查到佢地係一group人  主要係做咩我未清楚 但我俾佢地瘋狂狙擊 每個po勁多負皮 正皮攻擊我嘅留言 負皮我嘅留言 依點我覺得極為恐怖 有一班人唔係嚟討論而係狙擊<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xhahpK2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxhahpK2.png&h=916303de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KjoCpL3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKjoCpL3.png&h=c2cf6120&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n多謝同我講依句野嘅人令我親身體驗依句野嘅意思  自律與自由(已改名做星野瑠美衣)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5MGgFjO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5MGgFjO.png&h=6ab71692&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ffe413ba419e9f9c76f2f9a23a86654d9b650651","tid":2228600,"uid":249170,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T16:55:13.000Z","msg":"好有心機"},{"pid":"ede2fb7cd03e44385f4c229df36a026bacc3ac